DATA
----
The committed series are derived from public official statistics, redistributed
here only as aggregate/derived figures with attribution:

  • IPC (consumer price index)
      - 1993–2006  INDEC, IPC Gran Buenos Aires (base abril 2008)
      - 2007–2016  Dirección Provincial de Estadística y Censos de San Luis,
                   IPC San Luis — used as a credible alternative for the years
                   the national INDEC was intervened (2007–2015)
      - 2016–      INDEC, IPC Nacional (base diciembre 2016)
    Accessed via the datos.gob.ar time-series API.

  • Exchange rate (peso/US dollar)
      - Official:  BCRA reference rate (dólar billete), via datos.gob.ar
      - Blue/informal (from 2011): Bluelytics (bluelytics.com.ar)

These are official indices and rates; only the spliced/derived monthly series is
redistributed, with the sources cited above and in pipeline/config.py.

Attribution:
  Elaboración propia en base a series oficiales del INDEC (IPC) y del BCRA (tipo
  de cambio), vía datos.gob.ar, empalmadas con el IPC de San Luis para el período
  de intervención del INDEC (2007–2015), y cotización informal histórica de
  Bluelytics. Fuentes: INDEC (www.indec.gob.ar), BCRA (www.bcra.gob.ar),
  datos.gob.ar, bluelytics.com.ar.
